Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Interfaces
  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Interfaces 
    Interface and Description
    mortar.dagger1support.Blueprint
    see deprecation note on ObjectGraphService.requireChild(MortarScope, Blueprint)
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    mortar.dagger1support.ObjectGraphService.requireActivityScope(MortarScope, Blueprint)
    This method is provided to ease migration from earlier releases, which coupled Dagger and Activity integration. Instead build new scopes with MortarScope.buildChild(), and bind ObjectGraphService and BundleServiceRunner instances to them.
    mortar.dagger1support.ObjectGraphService.requireChild(MortarScope, Blueprint)
    This method is provided to ease migration from earlier releases, which required Dagger integration. Instead build new scopes with MortarScope.buildChild(), and bind ObjectGraphService instances to them.
